TY  - JOUR
T1  - Multicommodity Network Flows with Probabilistic Losses
AU  - Aneja, Y. P.
AU  - Nair, K. P. K.
Y1  - 1982/09/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.28.9.1080
